title: Fedwiki Tools
synopsis: Here we list a few useful tools. See [[Changes to this site]].

title: Pigny
synopsis: Pigny is a commune in the Cher department in the Centre region of France - [https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pigny wikipedia]

title: Welcome Visitors
synopsis: Welcome to this [[Federated Wiki]] site. From this page you can find who we are and what we do. New sites provide this information and then claim the site as their own. You will need your own site to participate.

title: Youtube Transporter
synopsis: This [[Transporter]] allows you to import videos from [[Youtube]], complete with all their metadata. It also allows you to import playlists, channels, and all uploads from a user.
